    <briefdescription>
<para>Object used to issue a stop request. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>The <ref refid="classfutures_1_1stop__source" kindref="compound">stop_source</ref> class provides the means to issue a stop request, such as for std::jthread cancellation. A stop request made for one <ref refid="classfutures_1_1stop__source" kindref="compound">stop_source</ref> object is visible to all stop_sources and std::stop_tokens of the same associated stop-state; any std::stop_callback(s) registered for associated std::stop_token(s) will be invoked, and any std::condition_variable_any objects waiting on associated std::stop_token(s) will be awoken. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
